Okayy, usually when we go to nhentai we go to fap. But there's the occasional hidden gem of a doujin that has good story that not only focuses on the fucking. This doujin is one of them, it has good art, nice story telling, excellent character and good story pace. Furthermore, this doujin have the vanilla and wholesome aura if compared to other non hentai shoujo romance manga.

Overall a 10/10 in my opinion

I LOVE THIS SERIES! Skipped it up till now because I don't generaly like gender-bender stuff, but this is clearly the A+ exception. Nice art, interesting setting, great dialogue & characters, and a genuinely fascinating story. One of the best isekai fantasies I've read, hentai, ecchi or otherwise.
